::DarkMouse::

She watched Quickstrike walk out of the base and Scorponok go deal with 
Megatron.  She walked over to Lightmare.
"So how are you doing?  Uh, if you have nothing better to do, I can use your 
help in setting up some of the lights around the command center."

She gave  Lightmare a friendly smile.

"Yeh, I know it gets boring around here.  One needs to make friends were one 
can around here."

She started to head tot he console.
